CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=16546934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=099acddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=0a5fe8d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"774455b7410698aa60a783efbd154b6d6c5e1e89","tid":1742761,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"ppppp"},{"pid":"f9c0774f78a48bee42c06e1188d92368c353b747","tid":1742761,"uid":50021,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"冇得停"},{"pid":"e66699f4fdef192365f5d9a0b36a55b3f64da7c3","tid":1742761,"uid":15945,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:45:12.000Z","msg":"不如答下我星期日區選就算民主派贏曬全部議席又有咩效果先啦<br />\n分清邊條先係主線任務<br />\n邊有人會放棄主線黎打支線咁on9<br />\n和理非唔進化唔敢上街都無用㗎"},{"pid":"7a70d70ee86efb126e8a386d0a0d7e994c7f6a27","tid":1742761,"uid":29381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2907ee5d72e72e6203b7952552ec7da6bad9db5","tid":1742761,"uid":58434,"like":19,"dislike":19,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"如果你仲比對方有休息的一刻，滅絕嘅只會係你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"對面有試過無休息？人地抖多過做呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c32e09c4a2294d5e03523261a17eea417d1505","tid":1742761,"uid":308020,"like":0,"disli